  <description>
    <p>Transistor is a modern internet radio player built with Qt and KDE frameworks. It provides seamless access to a vast database of over 50,000 radio stations from around the world, allowing you to explore music, news, talk shows, and more.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create your own library where you can add your favorite stations</li>
      <li>Easily search and discover new radio stations</li>
      <li>Automatic recognition of tracks if is possible</li>
      <li>Responsive application layout, compatible for small and large screens</li>
      <li>Support for various audio formats and streaming protocols</li>
      <li>System tray integration for easy access</li>
      <li>Dark and light theme support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
